Title: Acquiring Aqirite
Description:
You there!

Have you heard of Aqirite? Valuable, versatile, very often surrounded by nerubians.

I need that ore, and I don't care how you get it. If a nerubian does try to stop you, given them a whack for me.
ObjectivesText: Gather 10 Aqirite and deliver it to Tarib in Dornogal.
CompletionText: Well, have you got it yet?
RewardText: Aqirite is always appreciated. I'll get it to where it needs to be.
